	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just wanted to add my 2 cp:<br><br>VERY TRUTHFUL POST!&nbsp;&nbsp;( Almost thought people forgot what those were)<br><br>If you want to play a char for solo abilities, there are better.  And even if you play a good solo class, still group, or at least helpl others in a group if possible.  I have 3 high levs now and cannot overstate the importance of a players reputation in the game.  I have two epics done to prove that your rep can help or hurt you.  Otherwise, just wanted to look in to this class more as I am thinking of beginning one shortly.  The rest of the post sounds very results oriented and definately makes sence to me.  Seems like a great post.<br>&nbsp;<br>The best part of being evil, when I do bad things, I have a good reason for doing them.<br>&lt;a href="<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=311916"&gt;" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=311916"&gt;</a> Lizalfos Deathscale&lt;/a&gt;</td></tr>
